00:24:21.730 --> 00:24:23.210
Should I post about this?

00:24:23.609 --> 00:24:24.450
Visible only

00:24:24.450 --> 00:24:25.450
to Jiang Chen.

00:24:28.188 --> 00:24:29.480
(Mr. Lin)

00:24:36.360 --> 00:24:37.160
Oh no!

00:24:37.849 --> 00:24:38.809
Sorry, I wasted it.

00:24:38.809 --> 00:24:39.650
It's okay.

00:24:39.970 --> 00:24:40.769
Answer the call.

00:24:40.769 --> 00:24:41.410
I got this.

00:24:41.490 --> 00:24:42.129
Sorry.

00:24:42.129 --> 00:24:42.632
It's fine.

00:24:43.970 --> 00:24:45.369
Hello, Mr. Lin.

00:24:56.529 --> 00:24:57.289
I've put

00:24:57.289 --> 00:24:58.490
the original file back.

00:24:58.809 --> 00:24:59.930
I'll head home now.

00:25:01.170 --> 00:25:01.849
I'll stay.

00:25:02.970 --> 00:25:03.569
What's wrong?

00:25:04.450 --> 00:25:05.809
You seem off

00:25:05.809 --> 00:25:06.730
since that call.

00:25:08.609 --> 00:25:09.256
It's nothing.

00:25:10.089 --> 00:25:10.728
Alright then.

00:25:12.690 --> 00:25:13.288
Ren Jiatong.

00:25:14.650 --> 00:25:15.849
I know why you want to win.

00:25:17.289 --> 00:25:17.809
I can relate.

00:25:24.609 --> 00:25:26.250
I didn't get your bubble tea today.

00:25:26.769 --> 00:25:27.970
But thank you

00:25:28.129 --> 00:25:28.776
for the walnuts.

00:25:29.569 --> 00:25:30.609
Thank your sister too.

00:25:35.170 --> 00:25:36.010
Take some medicine.

00:25:36.970 --> 00:25:37.890
I'm leaving. Bye.

00:26:03.890 --> 00:26:06.490
♪You said tonight's
moonlight is so beautiful♪

00:26:07.529 --> 00:26:08.849
♪I said yes it is♪

00:26:15.930 --> 00:26:17.089
How do you know I'm here?

00:26:18.049 --> 00:26:19.490
You didn't reply to my text.

00:26:20.490 --> 00:26:22.010
Your things are still there.

00:26:22.450 --> 00:26:23.369
So you didn't leave.

00:26:23.490 --> 00:26:24.890
So I thought that you might

00:26:25.089 --> 00:26:25.849
be here.

00:26:26.250 --> 00:26:26.792
I was right.

00:26:29.129 --> 00:26:29.769
Drink with me

00:26:29.769 --> 00:26:30.690
since you're here.

00:26:31.690 --> 00:26:32.450
So unconstrained.

00:26:33.170 --> 00:26:36.010
But it's only 5% alcohol.

00:26:36.129 --> 00:26:37.410
Trying to get drunk or not?

00:26:39.769 --> 00:26:40.730
I want to get drunk,

00:26:41.049 --> 00:26:42.450
but I have work tomorrow.

00:26:43.129 --> 00:26:44.930
I have review notes to write.

00:26:45.690 --> 00:26:46.609
So many things to do.

00:26:46.609 --> 00:26:47.890
I can't let myself get drunk.

00:26:48.769 --> 00:26:50.210
Relax, I'll drink with you.

00:27:04.849 --> 00:27:05.970
Ms. Bai said that

00:27:06.289 --> 00:27:07.890
I feel inferior because of Yan Fei.

00:27:08.569 --> 00:27:09.569
She's only partly right.

00:27:13.490 --> 00:27:15.010
The person I envy is you.

00:27:15.569 --> 00:27:16.168
Me?

00:27:18.890 --> 00:27:21.010
I envy you for having a lawyer father.

00:27:21.890 --> 00:27:22.536
En serio.

00:27:23.129 --> 00:27:24.690
You can do anything you want.

00:27:25.450 --> 00:27:26.250
But I can't.

00:27:28.970 --> 00:27:30.329
Remember when you asked me

00:27:31.089 --> 00:27:33.170
about the side job I got outside Jun An?

00:27:33.369 --> 00:27:34.250
You told me it was

00:27:34.250 --> 00:27:35.170
your dad's friend.

00:27:36.930 --> 00:27:37.890
Not just a friend.

00:27:39.529 --> 00:27:40.650
He's our creditor.

00:27:41.890 --> 00:27:43.129
My dad was indebted to his dad

00:27:43.529 --> 00:27:44.450
and couldn't repay.

00:27:45.410 --> 00:27:46.250
So I have to pay up.

00:27:51.690 --> 00:27:53.329
I suspected a little, but

00:27:54.890 --> 00:27:56.250
I didn't expect...

00:27:56.329 --> 00:27:57.529
That it was so bad.

00:27:59.650 --> 00:28:01.690
Let the seniors
handle their own problems.

00:28:02.289 --> 00:28:04.569
You don't need to carry

00:28:04.569 --> 00:28:05.569
such a heavy burden.

00:28:09.650 --> 00:28:11.490
But it was my dad's wish.

00:28:13.609 --> 00:28:15.010
He died eight years ago.

00:28:15.089 --> 00:28:16.450
This is the only thing

00:28:16.809 --> 00:28:18.329
I can do for him.

00:28:19.450 --> 00:28:21.289
I'm afraid that one day,

00:28:22.250 --> 00:28:24.329
all traces will be gone
as if he never existed

00:28:25.250 --> 00:28:26.529
in this world.

00:28:27.250 --> 00:28:27.890
No way.

00:28:29.329 --> 00:28:31.129
As long as those who love him remain,

00:28:31.690 --> 00:28:32.930
he will never vanish.

00:28:34.049 --> 00:28:34.569
You

00:28:35.970 --> 00:28:38.289
and your mom won't let him fade away.

00:28:39.089 --> 00:28:40.410
Remember me.

00:28:41.690 --> 00:28:42.312
¿Bien?

00:28:45.170 --> 00:28:45.930
My mom?

00:28:48.369 --> 00:28:49.289
She remarried.

00:28:49.890 --> 00:28:51.129
Just now I received

00:28:51.129 --> 00:28:52.529
a call from her current husband.

00:28:53.690 --> 00:28:55.129
He's actually not a bad person.

00:28:55.129 --> 00:28:55.769
But we

00:28:56.410 --> 00:28:57.490
hardly ever speak.

00:29:00.010 --> 00:29:00.970
Can you believe it?

00:29:01.650 --> 00:29:03.490
Someone who never calls me

00:29:03.490 --> 00:29:04.450
just told me

00:29:06.250 --> 00:29:08.010
to call my mom when I'm free.

00:29:08.410 --> 00:29:09.809
I always ignore her calls.

00:29:10.289 --> 00:29:11.289
So she's worried.

00:29:11.809 --> 00:29:13.210
She hasn't been well lately.

00:29:14.369 --> 00:29:15.210
It's absurd.

00:29:19.289 --> 00:29:21.049
That's why you're upset today?

00:29:23.930 --> 00:29:24.609
I'm not sure.

00:29:25.890 --> 00:29:27.650
But I have this feeling,

00:29:30.089 --> 00:29:30.690
you know?

00:29:30.690 --> 00:29:31.490
It's like

00:29:32.690 --> 00:29:34.890
everyone has rushed ahead.

00:29:36.369 --> 00:29:38.369
Only my dad and I are stuck in the past.

00:29:42.930 --> 00:29:43.609
Tengo miedo

00:29:44.849 --> 00:29:45.849
Me quedaré sin hogar.

00:29:47.410 --> 00:29:48.104
De ninguna manera.

00:29:51.849 --> 00:29:52.520
Me tienes.

00:29:56.369 --> 00:29:56.970
Estoy contigo.

00:30:04.490 --> 00:30:05.010
Es tarde.

00:30:06.210 --> 00:30:06.930
Regresemos.

00:31:18.650 --> 00:31:19.450
Gracias

00:31:19.970 --> 00:31:20.930
por hacerme compañía.

00:31:21.250 --> 00:31:22.849
No lo pienses demasiado. Descansa un poco.

00:31:32.410 --> 00:31:33.049
Jiang Chen,

00:31:34.089 --> 00:31:35.450
Quiero luchar hasta el final.

00:31:40.609 --> 00:31:41.129
Entiendo.

00:31:46.650 --> 00:31:47.210
Gracias.

00:31:51.849 --> 00:31:52.456
Buenas noches.

00:32:15.970 --> 00:32:16.730
(Un archivo clave)

00:32:16.730 --> 00:32:18.170
(falta en el caso Hong Da.)

00:32:18.450 --> 00:32:18.970
Ren Jiatong,

00:32:19.369 --> 00:32:20.129
¿Fuiste el último?

00:32:20.129 --> 00:32:21.609
¿Cómo manejar la carta de demanda original?

00:32:23.410 --> 00:32:25.170
Además de mí, Li Ke también accedió.

00:32:26.849 --> 00:32:28.849
Yo fui quien
tomó prestada la copia original.

00:32:29.210 --> 00:32:30.210
Después de escanearlo,

00:32:30.210 --> 00:32:32.129
Ren Jiatong también lo tomó para hacer una copia.

00:32:32.609 --> 00:32:33.730
Había muchos documentos.

00:32:33.930 --> 00:32:35.569
Los conté todos y los volví a poner.

00:32:35.569 --> 00:32:36.849
en la caja de evidencia.

00:32:38.010 --> 00:32:38.849
Luego me fui.

00:32:40.809 --> 00:32:42.170
Ren Jiatong se quedó en la oficina.

00:32:44.089 --> 00:32:45.490
S-Ella fue la última en irse.

00:32:46.289 --> 00:32:48.089
Sin embargo, no volví a tocar ese archivo.

00:32:48.769 --> 00:32:50.569
¿Deberíamos revisar
las imágenes de vigilancia?

00:32:50.849 --> 00:32:51.464
Sí,

00:32:51.730 --> 00:32:52.450
Vamos a comprobarlo.

00:32:53.289 --> 00:32:53.970
Lo hicimos.

00:32:54.450 --> 00:32:55.730
Pero colocaron la caja de pruebas

00:32:55.730 --> 00:32:56.690
en un punto ciego

00:32:56.809 --> 00:32:57.329
ayer.

00:33:02.930 --> 00:33:04.930
Como no hay imágenes de vigilancia,

00:33:05.010 --> 00:33:06.170
Debemos informar a

00:33:06.170 --> 00:33:08.010
Los supervisores del Programa de Búsqueda de Talentos.

00:33:08.569 --> 00:33:10.250
El señor Zhuang, el señor Song y yo

00:33:10.250 --> 00:33:11.369
se le ocurrirá

00:33:12.210 --> 00:33:13.010
una solución.

00:33:13.769 --> 00:33:14.809
Por ahora,

00:33:14.890 --> 00:33:15.650
Estás en espera.

00:33:15.970 --> 00:33:16.769
Durante este período,

00:33:17.329 --> 00:33:18.369
No asumas ninguna tarea.

00:33:41.250 --> 00:33:42.089
¿Qué pasó?

00:33:45.450 --> 00:33:46.609
La carta de demanda

00:33:47.210 --> 00:33:48.569
Del caso Hong Da falta información.

00:33:48.890 --> 00:33:50.809
Ren Jiatong y yo
fuimos los últimos en manejarlo.

00:33:51.049 --> 00:33:53.250
Sólo ustedes dos estuvieron aquí anoche.

00:33:53.690 --> 00:33:55.369
La evidencia no desaparece en el aire.

00:33:55.650 --> 00:33:56.650
Eres tú o...

00:33:59.569 --> 00:34:00.650
Así que lo están intentando

00:34:00.650 --> 00:34:02.730
para determinar
cuál de ustedes es responsable.

00:34:19.169 --> 00:34:19.752
Jiang Chen.

00:34:20.529 --> 00:34:21.529
Te vi regresar

00:34:21.529 --> 00:34:22.209
Cuando me fui.

00:34:22.770 --> 00:34:23.490
Ren Jiatong era

00:34:23.490 --> 00:34:24.529
El último en irse, ¿verdad?

00:34:33.850 --> 00:34:35.450
Deja de especular.

00:34:35.970 --> 00:34:37.049
Vamos a intentar ayudar

00:34:37.049 --> 00:34:37.810
Después del trabajo.

00:34:59.609 --> 00:35:00.850
Jiatong, tómatelo con calma.

00:35:01.169 --> 00:35:02.330
Todos estos grandes talentos

00:35:02.330 --> 00:35:03.810
He visto todo en Jun An.

00:35:03.970 --> 00:35:05.410
Descubrirán la verdad.

00:35:08.209 --> 00:35:09.249
¿Qué pasa? ¿Estás bien?

00:35:09.729 --> 00:35:10.490
Hazme un favor.

00:35:10.729 --> 00:35:11.330
Quédate aquí.

00:35:11.970 --> 00:35:13.930
Quiero recrear
lo que pasó esa noche.

00:35:14.249 --> 00:35:14.920
Entiendo.

00:35:20.249 --> 00:35:21.249
¿Podría ser que?

00:35:21.370 --> 00:35:22.930
¿Alguien abrió la ventana anoche?

00:35:23.249 --> 00:35:24.330
Quizás el viento

00:35:24.330 --> 00:35:25.689
voló el papel al suelo.

00:35:25.890 --> 00:35:27.450
¿Cómo pudo el archivo simplemente desaparecer?

00:35:35.569 --> 00:35:37.490
¿Crees que se destrozó por accidente?

00:35:40.450 --> 00:35:42.649
Li Ke estaba más cerca de la trituradora.

00:35:43.010 --> 00:35:44.089
¿Lo hizo?

00:35:46.970 --> 00:35:48.209
También podría haber sido yo.

00:35:52.450 --> 00:35:54.010
Me distraje contestando una llamada.

00:35:55.249 --> 00:35:56.729
Tampoco es una gran decisión.

00:35:57.089 --> 00:35:58.649
Luego volví a trabajar.

00:35:59.209 --> 00:36:00.330
Si hubiera cogido los papeles

00:36:00.330 --> 00:36:02.129
inconscientemente a la trituradora,

00:36:02.129 --> 00:36:03.169
Es totalmente posible.

00:36:04.609 --> 00:36:05.569
Pero no lo recuerdo.

00:36:06.649 --> 00:36:07.209
También,

00:36:08.529 --> 00:36:09.490
Bebí anoche.

00:36:10.529 --> 00:36:12.290
Por supuesto que quiero demostrar que no fui yo.

00:36:14.049 --> 00:36:15.169
Pero no puede ser Li Ke.

00:36:15.370 --> 00:36:16.169
Él no mentiría.

00:36:25.770 --> 00:36:26.689
Tienes fiebre.

00:36:27.649 --> 00:36:29.529
De cualquier manera, necesitamos evidencia.

00:36:30.169 --> 00:36:31.249
Tengo que encontrar pruebas.

00:36:31.609 --> 00:36:32.330
Estás enfermo.

00:36:32.330 --> 00:36:33.569
Deberías ir a casa y descansar.

00:36:38.088 --> 00:36:40.520
(Jiang Chen)

00:36:41.529 --> 00:36:42.088
Hola.

00:36:42.770 --> 00:36:43.490
Xiaoyu.

00:36:43.490 --> 00:36:44.609
¿Estás con Ren Jiatong?

00:36:44.930 --> 00:36:45.609
¿Dónde estás?

00:36:47.970 --> 00:36:48.930
Estoy en la sala de impresión

00:36:48.930 --> 00:36:49.770
con Jiatong.

00:36:53.689 --> 00:36:55.049
Sé que estás bajo presión.

00:36:55.049 --> 00:36:56.249
para demostrar tu inocencia.

00:36:56.410 --> 00:36:57.450
Pero tienes fiebre.

00:36:57.450 --> 00:36:58.810
La salud es lo primero ¿verdad?

00:36:59.249 --> 00:37:00.490
La Sra. Bai dijo que no deberías

00:37:00.490 --> 00:37:01.410
hacer cualquier cosa

00:37:01.410 --> 00:37:02.370
Durante este período.

00:37:02.370 --> 00:37:03.609
Simplemente vete a casa y descansa.

00:37:03.729 --> 00:37:04.850
Estaré atento a la Sra. Bai.

00:37:04.850 --> 00:37:05.970
Y el señor Zhou, ¿de acuerdo?

00:37:06.649 --> 00:37:08.290
¿Cuál es el punto de eso?

00:37:08.609 --> 00:37:10.569
Tengo que encontrar la evidencia

00:37:10.569 --> 00:37:12.169
y demostrar mi inocencia.

00:37:12.450 --> 00:37:13.850
Nada de lo que digan servirá de nada.

00:37:17.970 --> 00:37:18.536
Señora Bai.

00:37:18.689 --> 00:37:19.649
Ren Jiatong tiene fiebre

00:37:19.649 --> 00:37:20.930
pero ella se niega a descansar.

00:37:22.410 --> 00:37:23.649
No descansar cuando es necesario

00:37:23.729 --> 00:37:25.370
Es más estúpido que holgazanear.

00:37:26.209 --> 00:37:27.089
Estoy realmente bien.

00:37:27.569 --> 00:37:28.968
No voy a mantener a un aprendiz desobediente.

00:37:29.770 --> 00:37:30.376
Voy a escuchar.

00:37:31.290 --> 00:37:32.129
Me iré a casa ahora.

00:37:34.330 --> 00:37:35.129
Vamos a ver a un médico.

00:37:35.890 --> 00:37:37.729
No es necesario. Solo tomaré un poco de medicina.

00:38:28.450 --> 00:38:30.169
No es el fin del mundo.

00:38:30.450 --> 00:38:31.850
Tómate un breve descanso.

00:38:32.370 --> 00:38:33.450
Todo va a estar bien.

00:38:35.609 --> 00:38:36.410
Deja de consolarme.

00:38:36.649 --> 00:38:37.410
Puedo manejar esto

00:38:38.010 --> 00:38:39.490
No me molestaría en consolarte.

00:38:40.450 --> 00:38:42.609
Alguien me pidió que te tranquilizara.

00:38:42.649 --> 00:38:44.729
y llegar a casa sano y salvo.

00:38:45.729 --> 00:38:46.850
Gracias, Guo Xiaoyu, por tu ayuda.

00:38:47.689 --> 00:38:48.890
Ella es mucho más joven que yo,

00:38:48.890 --> 00:38:50.089
Aún así ella me está cuidando.

00:38:50.450 --> 00:38:51.450
Estoy un poco avergonzado.

00:38:52.729 --> 00:38:56.410
Ella no es la única
que se preocupa por ti.

00:38:58.529 --> 00:38:59.169
Gracias a ti también.

00:39:02.850 --> 00:39:03.432
Bien,

00:39:03.729 --> 00:39:05.129
¿La Sra. Bai le dijo cuánto tiempo?

00:39:05.169 --> 00:39:06.410
¿Tendrá que esperar?

00:39:07.370 --> 00:39:09.569
Dijo que lo discutiría
con el Sr. Zhuang y el Sr. Song.

00:39:10.410 --> 00:39:11.850
El señor Song regresará en dos días.

00:39:12.810 --> 00:39:14.930
Los resultados de esta ronda
se anunciarán entonces.

00:39:16.169 --> 00:39:18.089
Nunca te había visto tan nervioso antes.

00:39:23.850 --> 00:39:25.490
Porque no estoy seguro

00:39:25.490 --> 00:39:26.490
Si fue mi error.

00:39:30.410 --> 00:39:31.249
Incluso si lo fuera,

00:39:32.049 --> 00:39:32.970
No fue intencional.

00:39:34.930 --> 00:39:36.609
Odio este sentimiento de impotencia.

00:39:37.370 --> 00:39:38.689
Desde que murió mi padre,

00:39:38.689 --> 00:39:39.649
Me lo he dicho a mí mismo

00:39:40.930 --> 00:39:42.089
Nunca ponerme

00:39:42.089 --> 00:39:43.569
en una situación tan pasiva de nuevo.

00:39:44.370 --> 00:39:45.609
Así que pase lo que pase,

00:39:45.850 --> 00:39:47.890
Hago todo lo posible para mantener mi vida y mi trabajo.

00:39:48.209 --> 00:39:49.729
bajo mi control.

00:39:50.312 --> 00:39:50.890
Pero...

00:39:50.970 --> 00:39:51.689
Pero

00:39:51.770 --> 00:39:52.970
Eres humano, no un dios.

00:39:53.729 --> 00:39:55.010
No te esfuerces tanto.

00:40:15.089 --> 00:40:15.890
Estamos aquí.

00:40:15.890 --> 00:40:17.890
Toma alguna medicina y duerme bien.

00:40:18.569 --> 00:40:20.249
Mañana podría ser un nuevo día.

00:40:21.209 --> 00:40:21.729
Gracias.

00:40:37.883 --> 00:40:38.770
(Yan Fei a Jiang Chen)

00:40:38.770 --> 00:40:39.729
Misión cumplida.

00:40:40.010 --> 00:40:40.770
Pero no lo eres

00:40:40.770 --> 00:40:42.370
en su lista de agradecimientos.

00:40:46.729 --> 00:40:47.528
Señor Zhou.

00:40:54.209 --> 00:40:54.770
Señor Zhou.

00:40:56.010 --> 00:40:56.970
¿Puedes decirme?

00:40:58.529 --> 00:41:01.450
¿Cómo manejará la empresa este asunto?

00:41:03.169 --> 00:41:03.784
Como.

00:41:07.930 --> 00:41:09.049
Sea honesto conmigo.

00:41:10.010 --> 00:41:10.850
¿Qué pasó?

00:41:11.729 --> 00:41:12.370
Señor Zhou.

00:41:13.129 --> 00:41:14.450
Yo no lo hice. Tú me conoces.

00:41:14.450 --> 00:41:15.609
Yo nunca haría eso.

00:41:15.609 --> 00:41:16.209
No fui yo

00:41:16.209 --> 00:41:17.290
No sé

00:41:17.290 --> 00:41:18.169
Cómo desapareció.

00:41:18.169 --> 00:41:19.249
Cálmate.

00:41:19.970 --> 00:41:21.450
Este es realmente un asunto serio.

00:41:22.249 --> 00:41:23.290
Copias originales

00:41:23.410 --> 00:41:25.129
Nunca debe perderse, pase lo que pase

00:41:25.490 --> 00:41:26.529
